description:
Do you consider yourself fairly knowledgeable about the world of dogs? Do you yearn to be conversant when the topic turns to dogs? If you answered yes to either question,    You Don’t Know Dog   is for you. 

Have fun identifying dogs.  Educate yourself along the way, not just to understand your friend better, but also to learn the characteristics and origins of these intense, emotional creatures.

There are over 400 breeds of dog in the world today. Learn about these dogs that changed our history.  Spending some time to appreciate these dogs will help you understand why they are considered our best friends.

You Don’t Know Dog randomly generates tests that require only a few screen taps to complete.  View additional information about dog breeds and their characteristics. 

Support for the application includes a support website and a public forum for suggestions, questions and answers.
